OL,5,G2315 The Debrief with Dan and ROG
OL,6,     FDan Biggar and Ronan O'Gara were
OL,7,     Fnever short of a word or two on
OL,8,     Fthe pitch as players, and now they
OL,9,     Fteam up to talk rugby in The
OL,10,     FDebrief, as they analyse the best
OL,11,     Fof the action from round two of
OL,12,     Fthe Nations Championship alongside
OL,13,     FClaire Thomas.
